<div class="half-boxes">
  <div class="box box-image view-image-gallery right" style="cursor:pointer;background-image:url('<%= image_path 'Salon_Image_2.jpg' %>')">&nbsp;</div>
  <div class="box">
    <div class="box-text">
      <h1>Be In Business For Yourself, Not By Yourself</h1>
      <h4>Salon professionals choose Sola for many reasons: to create their one-of-a-kind salon culture, have more privacy with clients, escape salon drama and make more money, for starters. <strong>But mainly, it’s about freedom and control.</strong> Sola empowers stylists by alleviating the risks and hassles associated with traditional salon ownership. We provide high-end, move-in ready studios along with the support and tools you need to launch your salon business in no time.</h4>
      
      <div class="find-a-sola">
        <div class="container">
          <h3>Find the Sola Nearest To You</h3>
          <%= form_tag [:search, :results] do %>
            <input type="text" type="search" name="query" placeholder="Search by city, state or zip code" />
            <input type="hidden" name="stylists" value="hidden" />
            <button type="submit" class="button primary">Search</button>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- <p><%= link_to 'Testimonials', :testimonials, :class => 'button' %></p> -->
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="half-boxes bottom-border">
  <div class="box box-image view-image-gallery" style="cursor:pointer;background-image:url('<%= image_path 'Salon_Image_3.jpg' %>')">&nbsp;</div>
  <div class="box right">
    <div class="box-text">
      <h1>Your Life, Your Style&reg;</h1>
